SUMMARY:GRACS x NVIDIA: Talk + Q&A with David Brown
LOCATION:GDC 6.302 (Faculty Lounge)
DESCRIPTION:David will give a talk about his team (ASCII at NVIDIA), the work they do, and what kinds of students NVIDIA is looking for across teams, then host an open-ended Q&A. He will also cover how AI is being incorporated across NVIDIA and how software engineers work on hardware problems.\\n\\nView more info here -> https://utgracs.github.io/nvidia-gracs-2026/
